headline: Is NextEra Energy Overvalued After Its 18% 1-Month Surge?
summary: NextEra Energy is getting a fresh look from investors after the parent company of Florida Power & Light quickly moved from laggard to leader within the utility sector, thanks to its 18% jump over the past 30 days.
